data.description: Wonderful one story home on HUGE lot. Varsity Circle is a very quaint, quite street located within biking or walking distance from University of Texas Arlington. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is light & bright with a big kitchen, lots of windows, two living areas, eat-in breakfast room and beautiful wood floors throughout! Creek runs behind the big backyard with sprinkler system and large trees.  Has both covered and uncovered patio areas. Workshop with electric and a storage shed.  Exterior and Interior just freshly painted! New roof being placed.
data.whatILove: Big back yard and HUGE lot in the heart of the city. Property goes all the way back to the creek! I love the bright light that pours through the house and the beautiful hard wood floors. It's a quiet street with lots of trees.
